events.name: New Years Eve 2026!
events.description: Celebrate New Year's Eve 2026 at The Anchor! Join us for a night of great music with DJ Jermaine. Free tickets – grab yours now!
events.keywords: New Year's Eve 2026, The Anchor Stanwell Moor, DJ Jermaine, free tickets, local celebrations, party, dancefloor, great music, countdown to midnight, night out
events.about:
Join us for an unforgettable New Year’s Eve at The Anchor, Stanwell Moor Village, on 31st December 2025! Doors open at 12 PM, with the party kicking off at 8 PM and running until 1 AM. Experience a vibrant atmosphere as DJ Jermaine takes to the decks, spinning your favourite tunes all night long. 

This is your chance to ring in 2026 at your favourite local pub, surrounded by good company and great music. Whether you’re a loyal regular or just fancy a festive night out, this event promises to deliver the best vibes. Don’t miss out – free tickets are available for the first 75 guests, so grab yours now!

Make the most of your evening by arriving early to enjoy drinks with friends before the party starts. And if you get hungry later, we’ve got you covered with tasty takeaway-style food options to keep you dancing until midnight. 

With limited tickets available, be sure to secure your spot for this proper local celebration. Stay local, stay safe, and let’s celebrate together – the Anchor way!

highlights: Fun and traditional pub quiz format
events.name: Pub Quiz
events.description: Monthly pub quiz in Stanwell Moor. £3 entry, £25 bar voucher first prize. Fun, friendly competition for friends, families, and teams.
events.keywords: pub quiz, quiz night, trivia night, Stanwell Moor quiz, pub games, team quiz, Wednesday quiz, family quiz night, quiz prizes, traditional pub quiz
events.about:
Join us at The Anchor in Stanwell Moor for our monthly Pub Quiz Night — the ultimate midweek highlight near Heathrow. Gather your friends, family, or workmates and put your knowledge to the test in a fun, traditional pub quiz setting.

Hosted by resident quizmaster Peter Pitcher, our quiz features rounds on general knowledge, music, film, sport, and more, with something to challenge everyone. The atmosphere is lively, welcoming, and perfect for both serious trivia buffs and casual teams just looking for a good laugh.

Entry is only £3 per person, and the winning team takes home a £25 bar voucher — a prize worth playing for! With the quiz running from 7pm to 9.30pm, there’s plenty of time to enjoy a drink, share some food, and soak up the community spirit.

Family-friendly until 9pm and set in our cosy, dog-friendly pub, Pub Quiz Night at The Anchor is ideal for locals and travellers alike. Just minutes from Heathrow, it’s the perfect spot for a fun night out filled with trivia, teamwork, and great company.
